# ============================================================================
# Git Attributes Configuration
# ============================================================================
# This file ensures consistent handling of files across different platforms
# See: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitattributes

# ============================================================================
# Auto-detect text files and normalize line endings to LF
# ============================================================================
